                                        Table "public.attendance"
   Column   |            Type             | Collation | Nullable |                Default                 
------------+-----------------------------+-----------+----------+----------------------------------------
 id         | integer                     |           | not null | nextval('attendance_id_seq'::regclass)
 student_id | integer                     |           | not null | 
 class_id   | integer                     |           | not null | 
 period     | integer                     |           | not null | 
 teacher_id | integer                     |           | not null | 
 date       | date                        |           | not null | 
 status     | character varying(20)       |           |          | 'absent'::character varying
 remark     | character varying(255)      |           |          | 
 notes      | text                        |           |          | 
 created_at | timestamp without time zone |           |          | CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
 updated_at | timestamp without time zone |           |          | CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
Indexes:
    "attendance_pkey" PRIMARY KEY, btree (id)
    "attendance_student_id_date_period_key" UNIQUE CONSTRAINT, btree (student_id, date, period)
    "idx_attendance_class_id" btree (class_id)
    "idx_attendance_date_class" btree (date, class_id)
    "idx_attendance_period" btree (period)
    "idx_attendance_period_class_teacher" btree (period, class_id, teacher_id)
    "idx_attendance_student_date" btree (student_id, date)
    "idx_attendance_student_date_period" btree (student_id, date, period)
    "idx_attendance_teacher_id" btree (teacher_id)
Foreign-key constraints:
    "attendance_class_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (class_id) REFERENCES school_class(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
    "attendance_student_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (student_id) REFERENCES student(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
    "attendance_teacher_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (teacher_id) REFERENCES "user"(id) ON DELETE CASCADE

